cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a system for machine learning with large-scale data, which is a common topic in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new method for optimization (SA L-BFGS), which is relevant to the subfield of optimization (cs.DS). The use of statistical tools and the focus on fast convergence suggest that the paper may also be relevant to the subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experimental results using a data set from Tencent, Inc. suggest that the paper may also be relevant to the subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) or neural networks (cs.NE).
